---
title: Easy Double Mumbai-Spiced Fish & Carrot Ribbon Salad  with Garlic Yoghurt & Coriander
description: It’s good to relax and refresh, and a good meal can be the first step! Our Mumbai spice blend adds mild and fragrant flavours to delicate fish fillets. Served on a bed of crunchy carrot salad, this meal is sure to rejuvenate you at the end of a long day.

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving and under 40g carbohydrates per serving.*

image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/66c6a264b372008c572c368c-2d073064.jpeg
